Help BTS get #1 on Billboard 200 & more charts

Tracking for the 1st week of album & song sales & streams ends today at 11:59 PM ET in the US. If you haven’t yet, US & Puerto Rican ARMYs, please buy LY Tear or its title track today in digital or physical format. BTS is currently challenging the top spot on BB200 against Post Malone.
